snippet.title: Monopoly Plus: My Little Pony DLC - Xbox One Gameplay
snippet.description:
As one of the three themed DLC packs, this skin of the classic Monopoly board is themed after the popular TV series, My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic. Also includes a Rainbow Dash token.

Monopoly (C) Hasbro
Monopoly Plus (C) Ubisoft
My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic (C) Hasbro
Also available on Xbox 360 (Backward compatible on Xbox One), PlayStation 3, PlayStation 4, Nintendo Switch and PC.
